Vivo Energy Cote d’Ivoire SA Company Profile

 
			

Get an in-depth profile of Vivo Energy Cote d’Ivoire SA, including a general overview of the company's business and key management, as well as employee data and location and contact information.









 


IndustryOil & Gas Operations
SectorEnergy
Employees-
Equity TypeORD


Vivo Energy Cote d'Ivoire SA, formerly known also as Shell Ivory Coast, is an Ivory Coast-based company engaged in the production of energy and petrochemicals. It is a member of the Shell global energy group. The Company is engaged in providing a range of products, such as fuels, including performance fuels, diesel fuels, hydrogen and bio-fuels, lubricants for vehicles and car care products, among others. Shell Cote d'Ivoire SA is listed on the Abidjan Stock Exchange.


Contact Information


Address
15 BP 378, Zone Industrielle de VridiAbidjan 15Abidjan, 378Ivory Coast / Cote d'Ivoire



Phone
+225-21-752727



Fax
21-272499



Web
www.shell.com




